      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You can get extra oomph out of your powered weaponry, at great expense to the weapon.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Engineering 5 ranks</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> As a full action, you can attack with a ranged weapon that deals energy damage and uses batteries or a melee weapon with the powered weapon special property. If you hit, you deal 1 additional die of damage per 5 item levels (minimum 1) of the same type the weapon normally deals. This attack causes the weapon to gain the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.2sVSvaOrr3uLW8Uq]{broken} condition. You can instead use this ability as a standard action on a qualifying weapon that is unattended or wielded by a willing ally to grant the same effect to that weaponâ€™s next attack before the beginning of your next turn.</p>"
